Detailed Description

DSS/MSS communication messages.

The structure defines the message structure used to commuincate between MSS and DSS.

int8_t MmwDemo_message_t::subFrameNum

message length : PROC_TBA does body need to be pointer and not a union structure?

Subframe number for which this message is applicable. Valid only when advanced frame config is used. When advanced frame config is not used, this field should be set to MMWDEMO_SUBFRAME_NUM_FRAME_LEVEL_CONFIG.
